      "content": "thanks for the info. i dont really want to deal with calling the surgeon right now, they're always so busy and it's probably just a tiny thing. if i just use the ointment and do the compress like you said, how long should i wait before i actually decide it's a real problem? like, if the redness spreads a bit more, is that still fine?",
